    "description": "故事发生在一只星际巨龟体内。在这款2D横板闯关游戏中，地图无缝相连。你会不断学习新技能，和其他角色一起探索这个梦幻世界。穿梭于奔流的血管；遍历闪闪发光的神经元；慎行于危险的胃区；感受这个世界的呼吸。加入英勇的治疗特遣队，击退虎视眈眈的星际寄生虫，保护这片奇妙家园吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强力的英雄小队</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 根据不同情况<strong>即时切换小队成员，</strong>充分发挥他们<strong>不同的战斗和行动优势。</strong><br></li><li> 在不同角色的视角下，解锁新的能力。<br></li><li> 不要抛下任何人！一旦有人阵亡，游戏就会结束，但<strong>小队成员可以随时解救陷入危险的同伴！</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/19bffa1f6435f4e518e333f322477a99.poster.avif?t=1755905849\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/19bffa1f6435f4e518e333f322477a99.webm?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/19bffa1f6435f4e518e333f322477a99.mp4?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界级生物</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索巨型星际生物奥拉斯克，在肺、胃、心等器官间游历。<br></li><li> 穿过错综复杂的血管，踏遍世界各地。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/599cc654b7b152376b8de965aa5af68a.poster.avif?t=1755905849\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/599cc654b7b152376b8de965aa5af68a.webm?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/599cc654b7b152376b8de965aa5af68a.mp4?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的敌人</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 体验紧张刺激的战斗，打败寄生虫大军。<br></li><li> 挑战可怕的头目，进行多阶段对决，家园命运由你守护。<br></li><li> 敌人首领拥有撕裂现实的力量，粉碎他的阴谋！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/ea29fa3c1635e9445be562e89e30c8e9.poster.avif?t=1755905849\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/ea29fa3c1635e9445be562e89e30c8e9.webm?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243250/extras/ea29fa3c1635e9445be562e89e30c8e9.mp4?t=1755905849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>流畅的操控，华丽的场景，由 Johann &quot;treehann&quot; Theo 倾心打造的配乐，《月色脉冲》将带你认识一系列令人难忘的角色，体验一场激动人心的冒险。<br><br>强烈推荐使用控制器游玩！",
